HEADWORD: cock-a-hoop
<hw>cock`-a-hoop"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Boastful;
defiant; exulting. Also used adverbially.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> boastful, braggart(prenominal),
bragging(prenominal), braggy, big, crowing, self-aggrandizing,
vainglorious.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

